      <section id="changes-since-last-publication" class="appendix informative">
        <!--OddPage-->
        <h2 id="h2_changes-since-last-publication" role="heading" aria-level="1"><span class="secno">B. </span>Changes Since Last Publication</h2>
          <p><em>This section is non-normative.</em></p>
        <p>The following non-substantive changes were made since the
          <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2013/PR-touch-events-20130509/">
           09 May 2013 Proposed Recommendation</a> was published:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Removed the <code>optional</code> keyword from the Web IDL describing the <a href="#widl-Document-createTouchList-TouchList-Touch-touches">createTouchList</a> interface, per <a href="http://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/WebIDL/#idl-operations">section 3.2.3. Operations</a> of the Web IDL specification.</li>
          <li>Removed “version 1” from the title.</li>
         <li>Added a <a href="#webidl-conform">clarification of Web IDL conformance</a>.</li>
         <li>Added a <a href="#stability-disclaimer">disclaimer regarding the stability of normative references to Web IDL and HTML5</a>.</li>
        </ul>
